---
description: Apply Spec-Driven Development workflow for new features. Use when planning or implementing features.
globs: specs/**/*.md, _todo.md
alwaysApply: false
---

Workflow:
- `/specify [feature]` → Create spec in `specs/XXX-feature-name/`
- Review `spec.md`, `plan.md`, `tasks.md`
- `/implement XXX` → Execute tasks with TDD
- `/review-implement` → Code review
- Track progress in `tasks.md` and `_todo.md`

Spec Structure:
- `spec.md` — Feature specification (what)
- `plan.md` — Implementation plan (how)
- `tasks.md` — Granular tasks with checkboxes

Avoid:
- Implementing without a spec for non-trivial features
- Skipping the review step
- Modifying specs after implementation starts without re-review
